# Introduction

Simply and fast information assistant application for Shanghai Disney.


# Features

- Display waiting time list for every attractions and performances;
- Add favorite for attractions and performances;
- Add schedule for performance to calendar with alarms;
- Display waiting time icon on map with its location for attractions and performances;
- Navigate to destination attractions and performances from your current location with route;
- Display the local weather and Air Quality Index (AQI);
- Widget display favorite items Information.


